{"type": "article", "id": 40989, "title": "把“纸”环在手腕上，就成了一个轻盈的电子表｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-05-18T22:53:43Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 247, "name": "Nendo"}, {"id": 40613, "name": "Paprcuts"}, {"id": 40614, "name": "Lorenzo Quinn"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 204, "image": "img/article/article_show/201705182147197F2ljXfyhxb4qT0K.png", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>PAPR by Paprcuts</h3><p>来自德国慕尼黑的 Paprcuts 是一家专门研发杜邦特卫强（Tyvek）制品的初创公司，由于这种材料兼具布料的强韧与纸张的轻质，加上防水和抗撕等特性，公司此前推出的钱包和手拿包系列都大受好评。这款名为 PAPR 的手表是 Paprcuts 的最新产品，搭扣处采用了磁吸式的设计，可以根据需要调节大小，电池寿命在 1 到 2 年左右。目前，公司已经为 PAPR 设计了 11 种不同的系列，有 30 多个款式可选。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/the-papr-watch--2#/\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，售价从 30 欧元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170518214747pqDHxXk0uyK1M9ne.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562903\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705182147464tkLb5VPIS3QzJUm.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562903\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170518214747NcEIw1lDLrF96SZA.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562903\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170518214747qKJfmwUlHghe41Oo.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562903\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170518214748yCD8ePvpFJAH4L3N.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666129\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170518214748T25MxR64PBrksez7.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667742\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Ballerina tables &amp; Lean vases by nendo</h3><p>提到大理石家具，我们很容易将它们与“沉重”联系在一起。最近，日本设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.nendo.jp/\" rel=\"nofollow\">nendo</a> 和意大利大理石家具公司 <a href=\"http://www.edizioni.marsotto.com/en/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Marsotto Edizioni</a> 联手打造的 <a href=\"http://www.nendo.jp/en/works/ballerina/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Ballerina</a> 桌子和 <a href=\"http://www.nendo.jp/en/works/lean/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Lean</a> 花瓶系列或许会挑战你对这种材质的印象。为了营造出轻质和悬浮的错觉，Ballerina 的桌腿底部被削去了一部分，看起来就像是舞者踮起脚尖。Lean 则巧妙地利用了圆锥和矩形石板相互倚靠的结构，让人误以为是尖尖的锥顶支撑着整个花瓶。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170518215301DIzJUEnueLjZOaH1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170518215259YLwNofC5s4qKvpcr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170518215300L26vT7ZJKC8DglIp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.498780\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170518215300RWJLfBlK6Qw3oAOz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170518215300smuP40SHCej7kNfI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170518215300BNaPZQLUj4wiCJ5F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667073\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Eco Deer by Kate Kuhar</h3><p>来自乌克兰的 Kate Kuhar 是一名热爱植物的建筑师及室内设计师，她在日常生活中就经常用枝条、巨大的热带植物或是花朵装饰房间。2015 年，她成立了这个名为 Eco Deer 的手工花器品牌，旗下的产品均由造型简洁的木板和试管组成，放入植物后就像是在模仿鹿角装饰品一样，看起来随性又自然。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/EcoDeer\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>购买到这些花器，售价从 45 美元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170518215319Gb9rYqBXhlZfFULI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667021\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705182153185tG0lpFkfYMZi86o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170518215319wC86Y2cNuTtRILUv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.344681\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>CYLNDR by Masamaro Fujiki</h3><p>在对电动剃须刀进行调研时，日本工业设计学生 Masamaro Fujiki 发现日立的 G-Sword 虽然采用了回转式的刀片，但使用时依然需要变换手柄方向才能完成剃须。为了进一步提升剃须的效率，Fujiki 基于 G-Sword 的设计进行了一番改良，带来了这款名为 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/51623995/C-Y-L-N-D-R-electric-shaver\" rel=\"nofollow\">CYLNDR</a> 的概念剃须刀。打破常规的圆柱形外壳内安装了双向旋转的网状刀片，只要沿着脸颊轻滚就能完成剃须。轻巧的外观对于经常外出的用户而言要友好许多，减轻了打包行李的负担。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705182153341kAvPWiuOlTXmbQ7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.647500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170518215334rD0R7j6tKBiUTqXH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.647500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170518215335R7aWKOxjrmAwhpQ1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.646667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170518215335wfminRZS76DOqjMF.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170518215335vzk4t1RP5WsjMVdp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.772500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Secret by Svetlana Kovylina</h3><p>在莫斯科攻读平面设计的 Svetlana Kovylina 以“隐秘的爱”为主题制作了一款名为 Secret 的概念甜点礼盒。通过最外层钥匙孔造型的镂空，人们只能偷窥到插画的一小部分，只有通过纸盒正面的小凸起将其抽出才能看到一幅关于爱情的甜蜜插画，简单却很讨巧。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170518215353G6CIXa4d8xwHPt7N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.567333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170518215353h6nlU7GVZFeD5WqX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.567000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705182153539Dbxcg8aSwBHAKXr.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.539000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705182153536cTqfd3m8HbGZLSO.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.568000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017051821535583W045nVZcGkg7wb.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.568000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Support by Lorenzo Quinn</h3><p>如果你最近刚好在威尼斯，在经过萨赛格雷多酒店（Ca’ Sagredo）时，会发现有一双白色的手从运河中伸出，就像是在支撑酒店的外墙一样。这个名为 Support 的雕塑是艺术家 <a href=\"https://www.lorenzoquinn.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Lorenzo Quinn</a> 为威尼斯双年展所创作的，他希望借此提醒观众不要忽视海平面上升对这座历史古城带来的影响，呼吁人们重视气候变化。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170518215430vTwFJClRZP1jo4fS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170518215429lB4HOwQnGgYrb0So.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170518215430OqE9vKrkzugj8Nl3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201705182154309uMm0D18fqxza7bF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}